image_analysis.description: A high-angle photograph of a luxury bathroom interior. The foreground features a granite countertop with a white undermount sink, gold-toned faucets, a white candle in a glass jar, and a bottle of blue hand soap. On the counter sits an ornate black and gold clock flanked by two small statues. A large mirror reflects the wall-mounted sconces and the opposite side of the room. In the background, an open door leads to another room where a large piece of artwork depicting a zebra is visible. The walls are covered in a patterned wallpaper, and the floor appears to be polished stone with a small woven rug.
image_analysis.layout: Interior room shot with a focus on the vanity area and a view through an open doorway.

stamps_or_markings: Bates stamp 'EFTA00000936' in the bottom right corner
A white label with the letter 'E' and some smaller, illegible text is affixed to the door frame on the right.

document_metadata.subject: Interior photograph of a residence bathroom

notes: The text on the white label 'E' has smaller sub-text that is too blurry to read accurately. The image is part of a legal or investigative production as indicated by the Bates stamp.
